Xarpolis posts some kinda pic that some mod called pornographic so it was deleted.  i didn't see the pic i didn't care.  but how one sexual pic gets deleted and the sexual sigs are ok? well i can only attribute that to the fact that those sigs are by &quot;respected people&quot; and the one deleted by someone the community loathes for not wanting to kiss your asses.  I don't care if you like him or not.  Here let me repeat that, I DONT CARE IF YOU LIKE HIM OR NOT.  What i do care about, is the double standard.  Elaboration to follow:  <br>
Everyone started flaming him and /ignoring AS as soon as xarp posted that first recruitment about not RPing.  Everyone used that to hate that guild and that person.  Like i said above Reso's RP section is 31 posts deep ~ guess what they aren't RPers, they just never told you that, so it's ok with you.  FnF didn't have an RP section till Ayida joined, and she's the one who used it most, there's like 1 post from a few other members.  guess what, FnF doesn't RP, they just never said it.  <br>
<br>
MY POINT ~ The majority is selective.  The majority is biased.  The majority is volentarily blind.  The majority praises the double standard.  The majority is in denial.  <br>
